title: Manchester Orchestra - Fourteen Years Of Excellence EP
description: "Fourteen Years Of Excellence is the fourth EP released by the band Manchester Orchestra it will be available on April 18, 2009[1] at select indie record stores as part of Record Store Day. A list of stores can be found on the RSD website[2]. This is being seen as a companion to Mean Everything to Nothing that is releasing on April 21, 2009 yet contains no songs that are on the full-length, besides the last track."
